<p class="ql-align-center">作为一名龙的传人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我感觉有责任去考察大英帝国的太极班</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200803/cf9428269b984ea494423e575203fafe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是我斗志昂扬地来到这里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200803/16fc41a416f0455d9ce126d2788ae415.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">教室里，太极老师已经候着了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200803/35df2a1178ca442aa26e3dfc98af7319.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但他的履历让我虎躯一震</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200803/66884f2a52e540ecaded7ad014d9e6f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">学员们自我介绍的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我仿佛来到《最强大脑》节目现场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200803/e1c6762c017947eeb09cd9c019a7e619.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我越来越沸腾了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">难道即将看到英国高手们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用东方力量进行身心灵的对决？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然而60分钟的课程开始了……</p>
